JMP does not report the breakdown between the SMDW and basic service level within subnational regions, and instead reports a combined category called ‘at least basic’ (ALB). To estimate the SMDW values in subnational regions, a simple cross-multiplication was performed using the splits at the national level:SMDWsubnational=SMDWnationalALBnational×ALBsubnational,\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
